{"tid":1903671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當大家捉緊鬼既時候，大量中共7人工會已經上線啦","createTime":"2020-02-29T06:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T12:21:17.000Z","uid":25825,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2d53136cc46142b00b4e1e294a3d4272393e06e4","tid":1903671,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"民間記者會發佈中心<br />\n<br />\n[🚨WARNING🚨]<br />\n我哋嗌緊交嘅同時，對家已經靜雞雞成立咗好多工會喇😫<br />\n<br />\n制度内顛覆work唔work？唔試點知唔得呢？係顛覆就要全面進攻，切忌佛系參選。以區選情況計，我哋嘅優勢係選民基礎，以量取勝。要贏就要快，將泛黃選民盡快轉化成功能界別選民。所以，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>組工會！<br />\n登記做功能界別選民！<br />\n<br />\n「7起」起工會神器：<a href=\"http://7up.hkpetitions.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F7up.hkpetitions.com&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT22mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=ef4f8674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://7up.hkpetitions.com</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔止加速組隊進度，仲提供會章Generator 及已成立工會會章範本！<br />\n<br />\n#登記咗先唔會少忽肉<br />\n#但到時想投無得投就揼春<br />\n#建造業關懷基金其中一個創辦成員係建造業總工會<br />\n#姐係工聯會屬會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkercpc/posts/206695227359879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkercpc%2Fposts%2F206695227359879&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT22mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=b5c5badc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkercpc/posts/206695227359879</a>"},{"pid":"4f4887388758829a219ad2f8e6416a7010891531","tid":1903671,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"，"},{"pid":"3aea3d7c54fc0801bb2b865cb336854e5d2fcf90","tid":1903671,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T06:17:58.000Z","msg":"，"},{"pid":"26f15261d6c2e8308bf28658a29fc016a486b104","tid":1903671,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T06:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=